<plot>The misadventures of Sicilian worker Saverio Ravizzi (Buzzanca), who escapes from being killed in a strike demonstration and eventually finds a new job in a factory in Bergamo. He begins to mobilize his fellow workers into better working conditions, unaware that his spontaneous activism is in fact being used as part of a large financial scheme by the factory owner.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?259403</url></doc>
